Name: Average time from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to Manuscript Export Succeeded
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded'

Name: Total time from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to SW-Checklist Completed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Minimum time from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to SW-Awaiting AE Assignment
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Average time between Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation and Plagiarism Originality Report Completed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed'

Name: Total resolution time of Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation and the end of the case

Name: Time until SW-AE Assign Reviewers since Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Average time it takes from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to the first Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1'

Name: Minimum time to SW-Reviewer Agreed after Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Time from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': "activity == 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'", 'end': "activity == 'SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit'", 'aggregation': 'total'}

Name: Average time for Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to be followed by Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission'

Name: Total time for all activities to occur after Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation until SW-Awaiting EIC Decision
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Minimum resolution time of Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation before any SW-Reviewer Declined event
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined'

Name: Time of Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation cycle until Manuscript is Withdrawn or SW-EIC Accept
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Manuscript is Withdrawn'

Name: Total time from Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation to Revised Manuscript Submission Confirmation in the case of major revisions
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'Revised Manuscript Submission Confirmation'
